text:
Privacy policy

We may use your information to personalize your experience on our website, including providing tailored recommendations and suggestions.

Privacy policy

We may use aggregated and anonymized data for research and development purposes to improve our services and develop new features.

Privacy policy

We may use your contact information to respond to your inquiries, provide customer support, and send you relevant information about our services.
We use the information you provide to generate custom supplement protocols based on your specific needs and preferences.
Our Zoom integration only collects meeting transcripts, which are saved anonymously in our S3 bucket to ensure user privacy and data security.
